title: What is Heaven? My Gifted Daughter Explains Where Heaven is, Angels, and Real Proof of Heaven
description: This is a true life account of a woman whose a psychic and her two psychic daughters. She has some amazing stories about different things that have happened to the three of them. What heaven is, where it is, what angels are, angel communication, all about spirits, and even how to attract luck and prosperity to your life - its all in there.
author: Hope R. Reynolds
